{"tid":789230,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【少奶奶生活】法國歎美酒！何艷娟P圖失手","createTime":"2018-08-22T05:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T14:45:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ec5e37a745aa22c9f1d331d52a75623c81daf5f2","tid":789230,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:47:42.000Z","msg":"喺劇集《宮心計2深宮計》飾演宮女嘅前港姐季軍何艷娟，自從下嫁澳博營運總裁吳志誠後，鮮有喺幕前演出。繼之前去曼谷旅行，原來佢近期飛到法國旅行，仲以一身高貴打扮去歎美酒，真係睇相都知佢過住少奶奶生活！睇番佢啲歎酒相，係打扮得幾珠光寶氣嘅，不過就有網友發現佢P圖P過火，搞到連階磚都歪埋！<br />\n<br />\n另外，佢又上載一張坐喺樹下嘅相，見着住短裙仔嘅佢大騷一對修長美腿，而背景仲係一間充滿特色嘅小屋，難怪佢留言話：「All nice and sunny down town！（好好太陽）」唔少網友都大呼好羨慕，話佢呢個闊太打扮而不失少女味，叫佢上載多啲靚相！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180821/photo/bkn-20180821091611364-0821_00862_001_01p.jpg?20180821135601\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180821%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180821091611364-0821_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20180821135601&h=efdda0e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180821/photo/bkn-20180821091611364-0821_00862_001_03p.jpg?20180821135601\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180821%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180821091611364-0821_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20180821135601&h=36e66cec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180821/bkn-20180821091611364-0821_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180821%2Fbkn-20180821091611364-0821_00862_001.html&d=E20NNy%2BV54F%2FbQl62HlGINU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=cf6a049b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180821/bkn-20180821091611364-0821_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6a8bd260688eb137eff4efa7269674eedfb0b130","tid":789230,"uid":13490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:52:24.000Z","msg":"吹氣公仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80f18ca85cda10dc2b1473976516da434e68fd2","tid":789230,"uid":145779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T05:53:33.000Z","msg":"臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6c1be59d2807541d81d121544b07283f21ed20","tid":789230,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:02:15.000Z","msg":"白到鬼咁"},{"pid":"fc3af8453031c02db780368172d185c353ebbff2","tid":789230,"uid":62815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:04:25.000Z","msg":"何妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b340addcbab6330e06f974b26ccdfaea88b7c666","tid":789230,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:05:37.000Z","msg":"睇黎睇去都唔多覺喎"},{"pid":"8fe01e0b9558026b36c536524dff112e25d56957","tid":789230,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc3af8453031c02db780368172d185c353ebbff2","tid":789230,"uid":62815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:04:25.000Z","msg":"何妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T14:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}